---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Blog
description: Articles about theme park maps, entertainment history, and collecting.
---

<section class="page-hero compact-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>From the Blog</h1>
    <p>Notes on park history, entertainment design, collecting, and the odd little details hidden in old guide maps.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="content-band">
  <div class="container blog-grid">
    {% for post in collections.posts %}
      <article class="blog-card">
        <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }} placeholder image">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
          <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
          <p>{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
          <small>{{ post.date | dateDisplay }}</small>
        </div>
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
